commit.message: doc: update url of submodule in BUILDING

Fix default set MKD_NOSTYLE flag

This allows by default to use `<style>` tags in markdown.
The tests did not fail because the upstream lib does
not filter inline `<style>` tags. (Probably a bug)

Fix the filter_styles flag to actually filter styles.

Fix #149
Fixing test:conformance:1.0 and run 1.0 and 1.0.3 by default

Update discount to 2.2.7c

Fixes #148

- Update submodule to tag 2.2.7c
  (Version 2.2.7c is not actually tagged)
- Update ext module with rake gather
- add -DBRANCH to build process
- Changed behaviour for toc character escape
  eg. A?B is now #A-3f-B and not #A.B
  see test/rdiscount_test.rb
  (Fixes #129)
